<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قُلتُ:</span> وذكره ابن حبَّان في <span style="color:#950000">"الثقات"</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٨/ ٥٠٩)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
